libcaptury: libcaptury (A library for X11/OpenGL video capturing framework)
libcaptury:
libcaptury: Captury is a realtime multimedia capturing framework for currently
libcaptury: OpenGL video (to be extended to XShm and audio/alsa soon).
libcaptury: Its uses are e.g. for capturing video from external OpenGL
libcaptury: applications (via captury itself) and is currently also used by KDE's
libcaptury: kwin to record your desktop efficiently (VideoRecord plugin).
libcaptury:
libcaptury: http://gitorious.org/projects/libcaptury/
